title: JSW MG Motor names 1st electric CUV as MG Windsor
description: JSW MG Motor India has announced that its first electric CUV (Crossover Utility Vehicle) will be named the MG Windsor. This follows a joint venture agreement with SAIC Motor to boost MG Motor's growth in India.
